headline: Caesars Virginia Opens Dec. 12, 2024
summary: DANVILLE, Va., November 07, 2024--Caesars Virginia is excited to announce its highly anticipated opening date will be Thursday, Dec. 12, 2024. The resort will welcome its first guests beginning at noon. Additional details on the opening festivities will be announced at a later date.
